{% comment %}
  VocalIA Voice Assistant — Shopify Integration
  =============================================
  Version: 1.0.0
  Docs: https://vocalia.ma/integrations

  INSTALLATION:
  1. In Shopify Admin → Online Store → Themes → Actions → Edit code
  2. Open layout/theme.liquid
  3. Paste this snippet just before </body>
  4. Replace YOUR_TENANT_ID with your actual Tenant ID from https://vocalia.ma/app/client/settings.html
  5. Save and preview your store

  WIDGET TYPE:
  - voice-widget-ecommerce.js → product search, cart recovery, recommendations
  - voice-widget-b2b.js → lead qualification, B2B service business

  IMPORTANT: Add your Shopify domain (yourstore.myshopify.com AND your custom domain)
  to Allowed Origins in your VocalIA dashboard → Settings → Allowed Origins.
{% endcomment %}

{% comment %} VocalIA Voice Assistant {% endcomment %}
<script
  src="https://vocalia.ma/voice-assistant/voice-widget-ecommerce.js"
  data-vocalia-tenant="YOUR_TENANT_ID"
  defer>
</script>
